description: Los Angelenos sure are in luck that the winner of San Francisco's Best Food Truck is now roaming it’s way through LA. They're steaming and baking up beautiful Asian Street Buns that are so tasty, they will absolutely make your day. So let’s cheer on The Chairman! Yaaaay!Their menu features a sensational selection of boldly flavorful Buns, including:Coca-Cola Braised Pork- with Savoy Cabbage, Preserved Mustard Seeds, and Garlic MayoMiso Cured Tofu- Tofu, Mayo, and Baby Choy-SumMuscovy Duck Confit Terrine- Green Papaya, Orange Pickled Red Onions, and Mint (just to name a few)All made exclusively with top-quality ingredients and spices, so of course it’s no wonder these buns are so deliciously addictive.  For bunches of quality and flavor, choose to munch on the buns from The Chairman for your next lunch.
name: The Chairman LA
